Interface ReportListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CurrentLevelBridgeListeners, MeasuredValueBridgeListeners, OccupancyBridgeListeners, OnOffBridgeListeners, PresentValueBridgeListeners, ToleranceBridgeListeners

    public interface ReportListener
    This class represent interface that must be implemented to be reported by driver, according to the Reporter where this object is added to.
